yzantin : L'Empire byzantin (641-1204) |volume=4 |trans-title=The Byzantine World: The Byzantine Empire (641-1204) |series=Nouvelle Clio \u2014 L\u2019histoire et ses probl\u00e8mes |language=fr |location=Paris |publisher= |isbn=978-2-13-052007-8 |pages=23\u201342}}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |last=Cowe |first=S. Peter |authorlink=S. Peter Cowe |date=2000 |chapter=Relations Between the Kingdoms of Vaspurakan and Ani |title=Armenian Van/Vaspourakan |location=Costa Meza |publisher=Mazda |isbn=9781568591308 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/armenianvanvaspu00rich/page/73 73\u201385] |chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/armenianvanvaspu00rich/page/73 }}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |last1=Donab\u00e9dian |first1=Patrick |last2=Thierry |first2=Jean-Michel |authorlink2=Jean-Michel Thierry |year=1987 |title=Les arts arm\u00e9niens |trans-title=The Armenian Arts |language=fr |location=Paris |publisher=\u00c9ditions Mazenod |isbn=2-85088-017-5}}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |last=Dorfman-Lazarev |first=Igor |year=2004 |title=Arm\u00e9niens et Byzantins \u00e0 l'\u00e9poque de Photius : Deux d\u00e9bats th\u00e9ologiques apr\u00e8s le triomphe de l'orthodoxie |trans-title=Armenians and Byzantines in the Time of Photius: Two Theological Debates After the Triumph of the Orthodoxy |language=fr |location=Louvain |publisher=Peeters Publishers |isbn=978-90-429-1412-4}}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |last=Durand |first=Jannic |year=2007 |chapter=Reliquaires et orf\u00e8vrerie liturgique |trans-chapter=Reliquaries and Liturgical Goldsmithery |title=Armenia sacra \u2014 M\u00e9moire chr\u00e9tienne des Arm\u00e9niens (IV<sup>e</sup> \u2011 XVIII<sup>e</sup> si\u00e8cle) |trans-title=Sacred Armenia \u2013 Christian Memory of Armenians (4th - 18th Centuries) |language=fr |location=Paris |publisher=Somogy / Mus\u00e9e du Louvre |isbn=978-2-7572-0066-7 |pages=198\u2013225}}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |last=Garso\u00efan |first=Nina |year=2004 |origyear=First published 1997 |chapter= The Independent 